Package: usefulR
Type: Package
Title: Cleansing Functions for R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rachel Hatcherian
Maintainer: <rachelsorice@usf.edu>
Description: This R package contains the functions I end up using the most.
    naReplace to replace the NA's in a given data frame
    numberize to convert test to number and remove both commas and spaces
    pMiss to calculate the percentage missing in a given vector
    rename to quickly rename columns in a given data frame
    columnSpaceRemove removes the spaces in column headers
    packageLoader takes a vector of package names and installs/loads them
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
